description: Cunning bottom cut-outs on these blocks fit most vehicle’s factory racks, as well as Thule® and Yakima® bars. Shaped to fit a kayak hull.Non-skid material laminated to bottom of foam to protect the top of your car.Dimensions are 10 x 10 x 41cm long.Sold in pairs.
name: Sherpak Universal Kayak Foam Blocks
